Unknown</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/t21ma2r</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kickarr]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Shout out to my friend Sara</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CfrYYR5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VG74vmF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>"Excuse my annoyingly happy grin, but wow, my sister and I just acquired these (very) early works by my grandfather, Frank Frazetta. He painted these when he was 10! 10!!! Insane."

