Let's get this bread.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HqjDF2I.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Pz96rk1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>*sips raki and coffee watching flame war in the comments as the comments section balkanize*</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e5B4mTe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>On a whim, i added dried rose petals to my coffee, which is a self-made blend of about 75% light roast Ethiopian Yirgchaffe and 25 percent Guatamalan medium roast.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V8bIfAg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pippin, 24/7.  (Actually, can someone more talented than me photoshop Pippin's head on the dude above on this meme?)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nJdBcQ7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I am trying.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7ejTPaC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FYmOkh4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'd get a happy meal for this</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/g2o0rwg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This and the isle at church for the Easter Procession on May 5th* are the only isles I see myself walking down anytime in the next year 

(*Eastern Orthodox, remember?)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PisQ3p7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me, this whole week, especially after Urgent Care decided after wasting three hours of my life NOT to give me a physical because I've been prescribed Lithium.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UvfiYjh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hyDm2Tm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dBSPnho.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It would be nice.  But I finally have an appointment with an actual doctor tomorrow at 10.  Which means I lose four tours and associated tips that this year typically would come to around $80-per tour</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TIBU6MC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JoTzA1H.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oh,and the dishwasher STILL has not been fixed yet.  Qwmmrrrearrrgh.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/k3nWwoC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Barring this, if I had decendents, I'd ask my decendents to make me into a skull cup.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9ksNHma.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me on Mondays, actually, but yeah</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ARFHvN9.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>As alternative life choices go, if more waters existed in Arizoma, this might be how I'd go.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V8JgNGp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KIhAHd1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/58Ctjhl.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Awwww, fine.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KIwBD2k.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jeBhuyg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oh, FYROM.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MeqJoMa.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/goYstsj.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me then... and now.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KFOnQfM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Yu1BEiK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Mood.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jiMOmpH.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bznL3dr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zB9lIBc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4GZxF1w.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>"Well shit."</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5HLGHEZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hahahahaha</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/64VGbKb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ytaTcGe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>..... fuck.  

Also this has BIG @kirbyvictorious book vibes...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sntmGbH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yIwCx1B.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NDuE6PM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QBjJAf5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xxgVOYm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I haven't been kissed or made out for almost a year.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oRHqT07.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3ZFm4Yk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UR4v0Ox.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/to5c1Qh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qkWjPgJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/caMXFZe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/upTmywu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JimcAGF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I should have used Lavender instead of the rose petals.  The flavor isn't terribly strong.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/v5GaAdf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rlg51zV.jpg" style